    <string name="https_filtering_explain_body">HTTPS Filtering intercepts web traffic from your selected browsers and applies cosmetic CSS rules to hide ad banners, overlays, and other visual ad elements on web pages.\n\nTo do this, a local Root CA certificate must be installed on your device. This certificate is generated locally and never leaves your phone. Banking apps, Google, and other sensitive services are never intercepted.</string>
